    Class Description
    ArgumentExceptionConverter
    Converts all ArgumentParseExceptions into localized InvalidUsageExceptions.
    CommandHandler
    Handles MyWarp's commands.
    ExceptionConverter
    Converts specific Exceptions into human readable CommandExceptions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ExceedsInitiatorLimitException
    Indicates that an action exceeds or would exceed the limit of the initiator himself.
    ExceedsLimitException
    Indicates that an action exceeds a limit of somebody else than the initiator.
